about this?</i>

00:06:53.246 --> 00:06:55.582
<i>I'm used to stuff like this,
remember?</i>

00:06:55.615 --> 00:06:57.918
<i>I'm the one who set my sights
on this career!</i>

00:06:57.952 --> 00:07:00.154
